'''奧羅維爾水壩'''（{{lang-en|Oroville Dam}}）為位於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[奥罗维尔_(加利福尼亚州)|奥罗维尔]]，攔截[[羽毛河|羽毛河]]河水蓄水的土石壩，壩高{{convert|770|ft|m}}，為美國最高的水壩<ref>{{cite web 
 |url=http://www.ussdams.org/uscold_s.html 
 |title=Dam, Hydropower and Reservoir Statistics 
 |publisher=United States Society on Dams 
 |work= 
 |date= 
 |accessdate=2012-03-31 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120325153036/http://www.ussdams.org/uscold_s.html 
 |archivedate=2012-03-25 
 }}</ref>，主要功能為供水、發電及防洪，該壩形成的[[奧羅維爾湖|奧羅維爾湖]]為加州第二大人工湖，蓄水量達350萬英畝-英尺（4.4 km<sup>3</sup>），为美国第21大蓄水量的水库<ref name="Over 40000!">{{cite web |url=http://cee.engr.ucdavis.edu/faculty/lund/dams/DamList.htm |title=Alphabetical List of California Dams (Over 40,000 acre feet) |publisher=University of California Davis |work=Civil and Environmental Engineering |date= |accessdate=2012-03-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205223601/http://cee.engr.ucdavis.edu/faculty/lund/dams/DamList.htm |archivedate=2012-02-05 }}</ref>。

奧羅維爾水壩由{{tsl|en|California Department of Water Resources|加州水資源局}}建造，為[[加州水資源計畫|加州水資源計畫]]的關鍵工程，為加州兩大水資源系統計畫之一。

==历史==
奧羅維爾水壩於1961年開始建造，建造過程中雖面臨多次洪水以及建壩材料運輸火車事故，大壩仍於1967年完成，整個工程於1968年投入使用。奧羅維爾水壩裝設[[抽水蓄能电站|抽水蓄能电站]]進行發電，該水電站為美國最大的{{tsl|en|underground power station|地下水電站}}。

===2017年洩洪道損害===
[[Image:Oroville_dam.jpg|thumb]]

====主洩洪道損害====
2017年2月7日，在多天大雨後以{{convert|50000|cuft/s|m3/s}}的流量進行例行性[[洩洪|洩洪]]時，奧羅維爾水壩的主洩洪道出現了一個大坑<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kasler|first1=Dale|last2=Sabalow|first2=Ryan|last3=Reese|first3=Phillip|title=Crater in Oroville Dam spillway will continue to grow, officials warn, as reservoir levels climb|url=http://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article131579999.html|accessdate=2017-02-09|publisher=Sacramento Bee|archive-date=2019-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807072128/https://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article131579999.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高入水量迫使水壩管理者繼續使用損害的主洩洪道，但這也使得坑洞持續擴大。至2月10日時主洩洪道的坑洞已達{{convert|300|ft|m|0}}寬、{{convert|500|ft|m|0}}長、及{{convert|45|ft|m|0}}深<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Oroville-Dam-spillway-hole-erosion-water-reservoir-10920358.php|title=Gaping hole in Oroville Dam spillway is growing, officials warn|author=Graff, Amy|work=SFGate|date=2017-02-10|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125083525/https://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Oroville-Dam-spillway-hole-erosion-water-reservoir-10920358.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，由主洩洪道坑洞沖出的碎片被帶到下游，造成的高[[濁度|濁度]]損害了{{link-en|羽毛河魚孵化場|Feather River Fish Hatchery}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.krcrtv.com/news/local/butte/fish-evacuated-from-feather-river-hatchery/326225498|title=Fish evacuated from Feather River Hatchery|first=|last=|date=2017-02-11|publisher=KRCR|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116042816/http://www.krcrtv.com/news/local/butte/fish-evacuated-from-feather-river-hatchery/326225498|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為了減低損害，魚孵化場的州職員開始撤離幼魚和魚卵
<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://newsok.com/article/feed/1165435|title=The Latest: California lake damage may near $100 million|date=2017-02-10|newspaper=NewsOK.com|access-date=2017-02-11|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914091649/http://newsok.com/article/feed/1165435|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicoer.com/general-news/20170211/amazing-engineering-feat-saves-millions-of-fish-at-feather-river-fish-hatchery|title=‘Amazing engineering feat’ saves millions of fish at Feather River Fish Hatchery|publisher=ChicoER|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505090016/http://www.chicoer.com/general-news/20170211/amazing-engineering-feat-saves-millions-of-fish-at-feather-river-fish-hatchery|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然工程師為了避免使用緊急溢洪道而繼續使用損害的主洩洪道，期望能降低奧羅維爾湖水位到安全範圍內<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://phys.org/news/2017-02-emergency-spillway-oroville-california.html|title=Sacrificing California spillway may avoid emergency releases|access-date=2017-02-11|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202043721/https://phys.org/news/2017-02-emergency-spillway-oroville-california.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但洩洪量仍從{{convert|65000|cuft/s|m3/s|abbr=on}}調降到{{convert|55000|cuft/s|m3/s|abbr=on}}，以避免損傷到鄰近的輸電線<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article132123804.html|work=Sacramento Bee|title=Use of untested emergency spillway yet again a possibility at crippled Oroville Dam|access-date=2017-02-12|archive-date=2019-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530224404/https://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article132123804.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.water.ca.gov/news/newsreleases/2017/021017oroville.pdf|title=Lake Oroville Releases Slowed to Avoid Erosion|author=CA DWR|date=2017-02-10|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213164326/http://www.water.ca.gov/news/newsreleases/2017/021017oroville.pdf|archive-date=2017-02-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但這也使得湖面持續升高。

====緊急溢洪道的使用和下游居民撤離====
[[File:Oroville_dam_spillover_2017-02-11.jpg|thumb]] 
[[File:Oroville_dam_infographic_feb_14.png|thumb]]
2017年2月11日早上8點，奧羅維爾湖水自1968年奧羅維爾水壩完工後，首度溢流過緊急溢洪道<ref>{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/wireStory/latest-emergency-spillway-oroville-dam-45401080|title=The Latest: Emergency Spillway Use Likely at Oroville Dam|author=Associated Press|work=ABC News|date=2017-02-10|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210163002/http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/wireStory/latest-emergency-spillway-oroville-dam-45401080|dead-url=no}}</ref>。水壩管理員和州水資源局官員當時認為不會危害到公眾安全，因此撤離奧羅維爾市居民並不被考慮。流經緊急溢洪道的流量達到{{convert|12600|cuft/s|m3/s|abbr=on}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Lake-Oroville-discharging-water-over-dam-s-10926950.php|title=Water flowing out of Lake Oroville emergency spillway|work=SF Gate|date=2017-02-12|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131202209/https://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Lake-Oroville-discharging-water-over-dam-s-10926950.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite tweet|user=CA_DWR|number=830837277987213312|title=Flows down the auxiliary spillway peaked last night at 1 a.m. at 12,600 cfs. Lake elevation levels are trending down.@CALFIRE_ButteCo|date=2017-02-12}}</ref>，直接流經緊急溢洪道下方的山丘，一如當初的設計。

2017年2月12日，撤離令被下達給居住在羽毛河盆地低窪地區[[比尤特县|布特]]、尤巴、及薩特等郡內民眾，因緊急溢洪道下方山丘出現了侵蝕洞，可能造成緊急溢洪道崩塌<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kcra.com/article/evacuation-orders-issued-for-low-levels-of-oroville/8735215|title=Thousands from Yuba, Butte, Sutter counties evacuated|last=Staff|first=KCRA|date=2017-02-13|newspaper=KCRA|access-date=2017-02-13|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114203847/http://www.kcra.com/article/evacuation-orders-issued-for-low-levels-of-oroville/8735215|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為了減緩洪水侵蝕緊急溢洪道，管理員調大主洩洪道的流量至{{convert|100000|cuft/s|m3/s|abbr=on}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article132332499.html|title=BREAKING: Fearing collapse of emergency spillway at Oroville Dam, Oroville evacuated|work=Sacramento Bee|date=2017-02-12|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2019-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809103345/https://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article132332499.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

到了2月12日晚上8點時，主洩洪道提高的洩洪量成功的降低了水壩水位，洪水不再流過緊急溢洪道，但撤離令還沒被解除。緊急損害評估訂於13日上午進行<ref name="SacBee20170212t2053">{{cite news|url=http://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article132360534.html|title=Experts: State left with few options while trying to avert disaster at Oroville Dam|date=2017-02-12|last2=Sabalow|first2=Ryan|journal=[[Sacramento_Bee|Sacramento Bee]]|first1=Phillip|last1=Reese|accessdate=2017-02-14|archive-date=2019-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807070238/https://www.sacbee.com/news/state/california/water-and-drought/article132360534.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至13日，約18萬8000名居民已撤離<ref name="SchmidtHawkins-20170213">{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/02/13/not-a-drill-thousands-evacuated-in-calif-as-oroville-dam-threatens-to-flood/?utm_term=.388358142d5d|title=‘NOT a drill': 188,000 evacuated, emergency declared, as Calif’s massive Oroville Dam threatens floods|last=Schmidt|first=Samantha and Hawkins, Dave|date=2017-02-13|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2018-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113224920/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/02/13/not-a-drill-thousands-evacuated-in-calif-as-oroville-dam-threatens-to-flood/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在水壩和洩洪道得到聯邦和州官員認定為安全後，布特郡警長於2月14日解除了強制撤離令<ref>{{cite news|last1=Daniels|first1=Jeff|title=Authorities lift mandatory evacuation orders for Oroville Dam emergency|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2017/02/14/authorities-lift-mandatory-evacuation-orders-for-oroville-dam-emergency.html|accessdate=2017-02-14|publisher=CNBC|date=2017-02-14|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119111118/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/02/14/authorities-lift-mandatory-evacuation-orders-for-oroville-dam-emergency.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====調查和重建====
重建溢洪道在2018年底完成. 2019年4月6日新溢洪道開始使用.

